lihkg.com/thread/330919/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n開冷氣都唔比，食屎啦你</blockquote><br />\n環保問題<br />\n同你而家餐餐食屎可以減碳一樣</blockquote><br />\n慳錢又唔撚得架？"},{"pid":"efbee4afe400e20b64b5733137449de5c82b53aa","tid":465394,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:05:49.000Z","msg":"用長者八達通"},{"pid":"5356f53071efc9cbf0cb18a89c04474382717ccc","tid":465394,"uid":4677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:38:55.000Z","msg":"仲有，漏咗樣嘢，輕鐵原站入原站出5分鐘內係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔扣錢</span>，如果5分鐘之後出站就會扣你4.6$<br />\n如果經同一個站確認左出入站，搭輕鐵巴士都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會有轉乘優惠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708460df2ce7003add18c59d92a69a5273f63cf1","tid":465394,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"整個app ok？"},{"pid":"8432e2ee1ce2375b7b59b3579ba5bcfe353969ec","tid":465394,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整個app ok？</blockquote><br />\n呢d民間智慧整完個app狗鐵咪block曬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b084a4052accf8e788253fac95e19e2f6e3b85","tid":465394,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"狗鐵揸盡香港人 但豪俾支那人先on9"},{"pid":"8615c40a9694cece90f3ae080226f43b2cb9c337","tid":465394,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗鐵揸盡香港人 但豪俾支那人先on9</blockquote><br />\n其實羅湖落馬洲應該再收貴d"},{"pid":"065dbb59142a9122d2e83c89c466c2bdcb645455","tid":465394,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"樓主發達大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc49488b9491ab7fc3a5dc7d9b74d721b768295","tid":465394,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"唔係住大西北，突然好羨慕有得搭輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60fb326deb417ed2be02b1d1a07a9fd225b36bb","tid":465394,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整個app ok？</blockquote><br />\n呢d民間智慧整完個app狗鐵咪block曬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會block<br />\n前幾年報紙報完都冇block 到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢啲駛撚整app 咩<br />\nRules 好簡單<br />\n1. 西鐵/廢鐵拍出站之後30 mins 內要拍廢鐵/西鐵入站<br />\n2. 巴士上車拍卡後120 mins 內要拍西鐵/廢鐵入站<br />\n3. 西鐵/廢鐵拍出站之後120 mins 內要上到巴士拍到卡<br />\n4. 每次輕鐵最多搭12 個站<br />\n5. 全部車程總時間加埋唔可以超過120 mins<br />\n6. 最多轉三程車: <br />\n    a. 如果轉三程車嘅話 第二程一定要搭西鐵<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n利申: 好耐冇咁搭過 如果有錯歡迎屌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}